{"tid":1551542,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"希莉艾維加盟《職業特工隊7》","createTime":"2019-09-08T05:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T07:24:45.000Z","uid":117117,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"798445b43d9a85616830d4f6dd7405c4e2cd562d","tid":1551542,"uid":117117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】先後執導第5、6集《職業特工隊》的基斯杜化麥格里（Christopher McQuarrie），昨日透過社交媒體上載《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》女星希莉艾維（Hayley Atwell）的黑白照片，並留言問她會否接受邀請？她隨即回應：「我接受，但我並不喜歡遵守命令。」藉此宣布這位37歲英國女星，正式成為《職業特工隊》第7集的新成員，將會跟湯告魯斯（Tom Cruise）及莉碧嘉費格遜（Rebecca Ferguson）等互鬥演技。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fUJJWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fUJJWr.jpg&h=b19fb4a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgpE1JC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgpE1JC.jpg&h=3e4853e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cN2OU3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcN2OU3g.jpg&h=cd64de3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91DxPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91DxPY.jpg&h=f347d71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0672f5f7d43bbfae7396c32eef2138487d474046","tid":1551542,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"blackmirror睇到扯左"},{"pid":"43697d198179cfb3a9dae02b5c8936bc419214d6","tid":1551542,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"The face looks so old."},{"pid":"1ef9da57b1389bdab8afbe4968d0ad8660f0acf3","tid":1551542,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be10